The Herald Blessings Chidakwa
Municipal Reporter Harare City Council town clerk Engineer Hosiah Chisango has been arrested this afternoon in Gweru over alleged land scams. Chisango, who was arrested while attending a town clerks’ forum in Gweru is currently detained at Gweru Central Police station. Special Anti-Corruption Unit Head Tabani Mpofu confirmed the arrest. “Yes, l can confirm that Chisango has been arrested in connection with land scams, but finer details will be availed later,” he said.